Step 1. Start

Step 2. Define function as f(x)

Step 3. Input initial guesses (x0 and x1),
   tolerable error (e) and maximum iteration (N)

Step 4. Initialize iteration counter i = 1

Step 5. If f(x0) = f(x1) then print "Mathematical Error" 
   and goto (11) otherwise goto (6) 

Step 6. Calcualte x2 = x1 - (x1-x0) * f(x1) / ( f(x1) - f(x0) )

Step 7. Increment iteration counter i = i + 1

Step 8. If i >= N then print "Not Convergent" 
   and goto (11) otherwise goto (9) 

Step 9. If |f(x2)| > e then set x0 = x1, x1 = x2 
   and goto (5) otherwise goto (10)

Step 10. Print root as x2

Step 11. Stop
